Run this:

    ruby run [name of benchmark] --times N --repeat R

--times runs the example N times inside of the benchmark
--repeat repeats the whole benchmark R times

For Multi-Core benchmarks, run:

    ruby run [name of benchmark] 'multi*' --times N --input [size in MB] --chunks [chunk size in lines]

To reproduce EuRuKo 2011 results[1] run (takes some minutes):

    ruby run [name of benchmark] 'multi*' --repeat 3 --input 160 --chunks 300000

[1] as presented in http://rubychan.de/share/supersonic-euruko-2011.pdf